# Installation

First you need to install InorigoJS in your project.

# npm

npm install @ortelius/inorigojs

import InorigoJS from "@ortelius/inorigojs"

# unpkg cdn

<script src="https://unpkg.com/@ortelius/inorigojs/bundle/inorigojs.js"></script>
